snippet.title: Mr. Fish and his Assistants Sardines / Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for the game "Mr. Fish and his Assistants Sardines"!This game was developed for the A MAZE. Museum Online Game Jam organized by the Leibniz Research Museums and the A MAZE. / Berlin 2021 - 10th International Games and Playful Media Festival.
